                ul
                    li Engaging in fraudulent actions or misrepresenting personal information
                    li Unauthorized access or tampering with user accounts or private data
                    li Distributing malicious software or participating in hacking activities
                    li Posting harmful, offensive, or unlawful content
                p.subtitle We aim to foster a safe and respectful online community, and we will take the necessary actions to protect the integrity of our platform.

            div
