            div
                h3.title-sm Contact Information
                p.subtitle For any questions or concerns regarding our policies, please contact us at 
                    a(href='mailto:support@fantasyhub.com') support@fantasyhub.com.  
                    We are happy to assist you with any inquiries or issues you may have, and we aim to resolve all matters in a timely and satisfactory manner.

    +Footer()
